txt.en: Gellamiel can be found in Ost Galadh.\n\nYou should speak with Gellamiel.
Roving Threat: Ghámgur, the Giant Dread
Elite lieutenants of Dol Guldur have been seen patrolling the hostile region of Southern Mirkwood, including Ghámgur, a brutal warrior with a thirst for death.
Ghámgur can be found somewhere in Southern Mirkwood.\n\nYou should defeat Ghámgur.

'Ghámgur, a powerful Gorthorog out of Dol Guldur stalks the hills and valleys of Mirkwood. His mission is unknown to us but perhaps he merely patrols to intimidate us. If you encounter this powerful foe, defeat him quickly.'
'The forces of Dol Guldur may outnumber us but our hope outshines all. You have done a great service for the Malledhrim.'
